{"tid":2191794,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"五十年不變明明唔係為左香港而設","createTime":"2020-09-06T16:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T16:20:53.000Z","uid":89500,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"299a6e18edc2868a76870b73ab1d7c090160514a","tid":2191794,"uid":89500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"基本法寫一國兩制，以往嘅制度同生活方式能夠保證五十年不變。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知一半都未到就變哂。<br />\n<br />\n細心啲諗當時咁樣訂立唔係因為鄧小平期望50年後香港遂漸大6化，而係覺得50年後中國應該同世界嘅價值觀接軌，咁自然50年後就無需要再改變。<br />\n<br />\n可惜事與願違，中共無變得好，香港最後變成一個中國城市。"},{"pid":"ecaa51b6be889c5cd8e797f35729eb0c6aad1094","tid":2191794,"uid":128102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"唔洗細心d諗<br />\n佢下一句係五十年後更沒有變的道理"},{"pid":"f11ec0634ca41601fc218ded2e7303565ef0d72e","tid":2191794,"uid":69866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"最失敗係香港人相信一國兩制"},{"pid":"a4fada43f569c6271445d8b0cbd1bb4c471a8fb4","tid":2191794,"uid":69866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:16:29.000Z","msg":"一開始就要set死期<br />\n某某年冇普選就視為違反中英聯合聲明，回歸返英國"},{"pid":"1ee79727adb33e7d453deea09ed1eed6aa3c690d","tid":2191794,"uid":332578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"聽日有手足還押已九個月 香港唔係得幾個人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2191764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2191764</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94b12a7612d8a156c249d67e3f8bb97a2e62dfb0","tid":2191794,"uid":118217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4fada43f569c6271445d8b0cbd1bb4c471a8fb4","tid":2191794,"uid":69866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:16:29.000Z","msg":"一開始就要set死期<br />\n某某年冇普選就視為違反中英聯合聲明，回歸返英國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"起碼要有呢個機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}